        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>numNeighbours</name>
        <qualifiedname>MR.TriangulationParameters.numNeighbours</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>The number of nearest neighbor points to use for building of local triangulation. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Too small value can make not optimal triangulation and additional holes<linebreak/>
Too big value increases difficulty of optimization and decreases performance &amp;lt;table border=0&amp;gt; &amp;lt;caption id="TriangulationParameters::numNeighbours_examples"&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/caption&amp;gt; &amp;lt;tr&amp;gt; &amp;lt;td&amp;gt;<image type="html" name="triangulate_3.png">"Good" width = 350cm &amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;</image>
 &amp;lt;td&amp;gt;<image type="html" name="triangulate_2.png">"Too small value" width = 350cm &amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;</image>
 &amp;lt;/tr&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/table&amp;gt; </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
